        <head xml:id="pl-l4d48c1-Hd1e109">Capitulum 1</head>
        <head xml:id="pl-l4d48c1-Hd1e112" type="question-title">De forma iudicis.</head>
        <p xml:id="pl-l4d48c1-d1e115">Solet etiam quaeri, in qua forma Christus iudicabit.</p>
        <p xml:id="pl-l4d48c1-d1e118">In forma utique servi indicabit, quae omnibus in iudicio
          apparebit, ut videant mali, <quote xml:id="pl-l4d48c1-Qd1e120">in quem pupugerunt</quote>.
          Divinitatem vero eius mali non videbunt; unde Isaias: <quote xml:id="pl-l4d48c1-Qd1e123"
          >Tollatur impius, ne videat gloriam Dei.</quote> <quote xml:id="pl-l4d48c1-Qd1e126">
          Humanitatem videbunt, ut timeant; Divinitatem vero non, ne gaudeant: Divinitas enim sine
          gaudio videri non potest</quote>.</p>
      </div>
